    "body": "1) I know you are not selecting on the column, that's why your use of the syntax is in effect a bug. 0.8.1 is a quite old version (and has had quite a few API changes/bug fixes since then), you should consider upgrading\n2) this looks fine. It is quite non-trivial to do a mutli-level assignment to the non-zero level. You are welcome to try to come up with a nice syntax for that if you would like.\n"
